        <div class="msgSubject">Been a while since I posted here...</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-18 09:16:39   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1290093399249907028" id="quote-1290093399249907028" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1290093399249907028" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=28&amp;mid=1290093399249907028&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1290093399249907028&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1290093399249907028" onclick="followToggle('add','1290093399249907028')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
