urse that doesn't mean you should take stupid risks, and i agree, actively texting while driving is retarded. However replying to a text or two while driving is incredibly unlikely to cause an accident. And if it <i>is</i> likely (like &gt;.1%) for a given person, then i've already addressed that concern. <br /> <br />People take risks/shortcuts that might end up costing lives all the @#%^ing time. Sometimes that chance turns into reality. Having sh*tty luck doesn't make that person any worse than everyone else. <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Nov 18th 2010  2:37pm by ThePsychoticOne </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><s><a href="HTTP://ffxiah.com/player.php?id=1580273#item-sets" rel="external nofollow" title="ffxiah.com/player.php?id=1580273#item-sets">Rog</a></s> <a href="HTTP://ffxirog.livejournal.com" rel="external nofollow" title="ffxirog.livejournal.com">lolLJ</a> <a href="HTTP://myanimelist.net/animelist/thepsychoticone" rel="external nofollow" title="myanimelist.net/animelist/thepsychoticone">Anime!</a> <br /><span class="sm"><s>75RDMBLMBRDNINRNG72(oc)DRK</s> <br /><a href="HTTP://www.ffxiah.com/player/Quetzalcoatl/Ahou#item-sets" rel="external nofollow" title="www.ffxiah.com/player/Quetzalcoatl/Ahou#item-sets">ROUND2</a>:85RDMBLMWAR75CORSMN</span><div class="msgQuote"><div class="source">Kerberoz wrote:</div><div class="orig"><span class="sm">If you constantly defend sh*t gear and whine incessantly about elitists, you are guaranteed to have neither skill nor gear.</span></div></div><div class="msgQuote"><div class="source">Usagi wrote:</div><div class="orig"><span class="sm">I </span><b><span style="color:hotpink">LOVE</span></b><span class="sm"> CP.</div></div></span><div class="msgQuote"><div class="source">rale wrote:</div><div class="orig"><span class="sm">#1... for number of times your posts have been reported by other people.</span></div></div></div></div>
