ght that there wasn't any problem with texting while driving.  He has a lot of remorse for the accident, hopefully he learned his lesson.  Going to go see her again this weekend and maybe see her son too, he's in the ICU so it's not as easy to get to him and we didn't have enough time today to stay for very long.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><span class="sm">The greatest trick the devil ever pulled was to convince the world he didn't exist. <br /><a href="HTTP://ffxiv.zam.com/wiki/FFXIV_Windows_Gadget" rel="external nofollow" title="ffxiv.zam.com/wiki/FFXIV_Windows_Gadget">Windows 7/Vista Eorzea Gadget</a> <br /><a href="HTTP://ffxiv.zam.com/forum.html?game=268&amp;mid=128102874375645847&amp;page=1" rel="external" title="ffxiv.zam.com/forum.html?game=268&amp;mid=128102874375645847&amp;page=1">Keyboard LCD Eorzea Clock</a></span> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/356033.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
